But what this is here is a layoff. A novel approach where the employee makes the choice.  And I don't know about Australia - ise laying off excess employees illegal?</p><p>

If you get a job in Europe or OZ, is it mandatory employment for your life, where you by law, cannot ever be let go?</p></div>
	</div>

